					<Text>
						<Options>2</Options>
						<StyledText>
							<Data><![CDATA[This file endeavors to have an example of One Of Everything (Ooe)—one of every possible configuration of every kind of solution element.

For example, every kind of layout part or layout object, every kind of value list, every kind of script step, etc.

Achieving 100% coverage is not a realistic goal, but the hope is that over time we can add examples of all these different permutations to this file.



Last updated: 2025-10-28
]]></Data>
						</StyledText>
					</Text>
